name: Yertle The Turtle
description: On the far-away island of Sala-ma-Sond, Yertle the Turtle was king of the pond. A nice little pond. It was clean. It was neat. The water was warm. There was plenty to eat. The turtles had everything turtles might need. And they were all happy. Quite happy indeed. From this wonderful story a meme play has been created. Ladies and gentleman. Welcome to $YERTLE..
